The [Las Vegas Strip](/Las_Vegas_Strip) is the obvious economic engine, a hub for gaming companies. Numerous corporations have a presence here, including [Golden Entertainment](/Golden_Entertainment), [MGM Resorts International](/MGM_Resorts_International), [Las Vegas Sands](/Las_Vegas_Sands), and [Wynn Resorts](/Wynn_Resorts), among many others.

